snippet.title: Johnny Depp libel case: Star found discovery of faeces in bed 'hilarious'
snippet.description:
The High Court has heard about a violent row between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp, with faeces allegedly being discovered in their bed by a cleaner.

Depp denied claims on Friday that he threw a bottle at Heard, grabbed her hair and pushed her down after the row.

The star said he 'laughed so hard' after faeces was found in their bed the next day, and said he assumed Heard or her friend were responsible.
